Determine the values printed by the following code:

```java
public class Box {
    private int size;

    public Box(int s) { size = s; }
    public void grow(int amount) { size += amount; }
    public int getSize() { return size; }
}

public static void enlarge(Box b, int n) {
    b.grow(n);
    n = 0;
}
```

```java
Box myBox = new Box(10);
enlarge(myBox, 5);
int x = myBox.getSize();
int y = 3;
enlarge(myBox, y);
y = 0;
System.out.println(x + " " + y);
```

